.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, lily, daisy, dahlia
1. the person who growsaconite is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who growslily is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who growsdaisy##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| Flower   | daisy   | lily     | dahlia | aconite |

