.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, snake, hamster, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the owner of the hamster is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Pet         | snake | hamster | pony | mouse |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

