.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, surfing, ice-hockey, soccer
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Sport   | ice-hockey          | surfing     | soccer  | snowboarding     |

