3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job           | doctor | librarian | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| City   | london   | paris | edinburgh         | marseilles |

