.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, lemonade, coffee
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
5. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | coffee   | milk   | water | lemonade |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

