.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, spy, mystery, family
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the owner of the cat and the person watching family movies##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | family     | documentary | spy |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 